{{!
  MERGE-IN SNIPPET - not a complete file.

  Add this <div> inside the existing tab-content container in your
  game's ares-webportal/app/templates/components/profile-custom.hbs,
  alongside any other plugins' custom tab panes already there. The id
  here must match the href in profile-custom-tabs.snippet.hbs.

  This is a self-contained invocation of this plugin's own
  inklings-tab component (app/components/inklings-tab.js +
  app/templates/components/inklings-tab.hbs) - it makes its own API
  calls and saves its own changes immediately, so it doesn't need to
  participate in the surrounding Profile page's overall save flow.

  Adjust this.char / this.viewer / this.isStaff below to whatever the
  surrounding profile-custom.hbs actually calls those properties in
  your install - these are the common names, but verify against the
  rest of that template.
}}
<div class="tab-pane fade" id="inklings-tab-pane">
  {{inklings-tab characterId=this.char.id viewerId=this.viewer.id isStaff=this.viewer.isStaff}}
</div>
